<div class="title">Midnight Madness</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines, Modafinil (Provigil), Indian Pipe Root</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Jay&Exact=1">Jay</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Jay. "Midnight Madness: An Experience with Amphetamines, Modafinil (Provigil), Indian Pipe Root (exp35999)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 12, 2004. erowid.org/exp/35999</div>

